至不足300萬，賬面蒸發約200萬元。何先生指，自己擔心騰訊進一步下跌，但股票升跌難以預測，現階段都是先觀察形勢。<br />\n他又認為：「如果蝕緊都唔賣住先，由佢先，希望佢遲啲起返多少。」他又認為股民現在應該持現金，不要入市較好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181011/large/1539241415_1c96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181011%2Flarge%2F1539241415_1c96.jpg&h=3a243914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n表示持有騰訊的散戶何先生指，現在出售騰訊會「蝕底」，故靜觀其變<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181011/58782338\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58782338&d=ivu1EHg7zyOx%2Bwb3cawZBrIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=81241505\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58782338&h=d2d25e2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181011/58782338</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:11:43.000Z","msg":"擺到兩腳一申都係得300 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676acf26bce821e4537e1af94d3e8365ae83a4cc","tid":857773,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T13:18:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正</span></span>"},{"pid":"8dc257d6b2bec89212846510fc9aade1d7009118","tid":857773,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6196f96933e0cffa0086b36565fe43b553162d8","tid":857773,"uid":60917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"39f495d594f98d69115cfab5289c1e0bb941ed50","tid":857773,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:22:37.000Z","msg":"騰訊今日重挫7%，表示持有「萬零股」騰訊的散戶何先生，對今日跌市表示擔心，並表示現在出售騰訊會「蝕底」，所以會靜觀其變。<br />\n以今年高位476.6元計，何生手持騰訊高峰期值約500萬元，如今跌至不足300萬，賬面蒸發約200萬元。何先生指，自己擔心騰訊進一步下跌，但股票升跌難以預測，現階段都是先觀察形勢。<br />\n他又認為：「如果蝕緊都唔賣住先，由佢先，希望佢遲啲起返多少。」他又認為股民現在應該持現金，不要入市較好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"ht